                  </persName>
             depos'd that there was nothing at all in it, his Mistress was perjur'd, that the Prisoner never touch'd him, nor was within two Foot of his Bed Side.</p>
               <p>The Prisoner call'd several Men and Women to his Reputation who depos'd but he was a kind Husband to his Wife and a careful Father to his Children, and always pretende'd the Company of Women to that of the Men - Many of his male bedfellows depos'd, that he never offer'd any such incivilities to them, and the Jury <rs id="t17260711-55-verdict256" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17260711-55-verdict256" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
